### About

World population statistics from 1950.

### Access

No bulk download. Can only download data for up to five countries at once. Available in CSV.

### Openness

Not open. [Copyright page](http://esa.un.org/unpp/index.asp?panel=8) states:

> The United Nations' explicit written permission must be obtained in order to:

>> 1. Use all or any part of the Copyrighted Materials for any Commercial Use;
>> 2. Systematically distribute the whole or any part of the Copyrighted Materials to anyone;
>> 3. Publish, distribute or make available the Copyrighted Materials, works based on the Copyrighted Materials or works that combine them with any other material;
>> 4. Alter, abridge, adapt or modify the Copyrighted Materials, except to the extent necessary to make them perceptible on a computer screen.
